// Embed the manifest that declares QLever executables long-path aware (paths
// longer than MAX_PATH (260 characters) work whenever the system has long paths
// enabled) and sets the process active code page to UTF-8 (Windows 10 1903+),
// so the narrow file APIs interpret paths and `argv` as UTF-8. Resource ID 1 =
// CREATEPROCESS_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID, type 24 = RT_MANIFEST (numeric literals to
// keep this file self-contained).
1 24 "LongPathAware.manifest"
